          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "今日里一心要捉拿奸曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹操到此，禀爷知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹操 （内西皮导板） 曹孟德在马上长吁短叹，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍、曹八将、曹操同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "手捶胸眼落泪苦怨长天。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "实指望灭刘备踏翻江南。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "黄公覆献连环火烧战船。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮慢板",
          "musical_style": "西皮慢板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只剩下十八骑好不可怜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "在中原领人马八十三万"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恨只恨诸葛亮诡计多端"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只烧得众兵丁皮开肉绽"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "坐雕鞍勒丝疆用目观看"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "丞相发笑为哪般？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "笑是笑周郎见识浅，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孔明袖内少机关。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "又恐失计难保还。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（龙套喊。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一声未发人马喊，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "旌旗招展心胆寒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "许褚看看，什么人的旗号？"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（许褚看。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那是“关”字旗号。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "待我谢天谢地！"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "事到如今，谢什么天地？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那关云长曾许我三次不死，难道今日一也次不饶么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣杀不得了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用你杀了，后面歇息去罢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "遵命。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听说来了关美髯，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不由孟德喜心间。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "问声君侯驾可安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "走上前来把礼见"
        },
        {
          "character": "小校",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "曹操到！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮导板",
          "musical_style": "西皮导板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "耳边厢又听得人嘶马闹，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽上台子。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "纵蚕眉睁凤眼仔细观瞧："
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奉军令谁认你旧日故好。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "狭路上莫不是冤家来到"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曹孟德在马上满面陪笑，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "尊一声汉君侯细听根苗："
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "望君侯开大恩放我回朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在赤壁中火攻败兵来到"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "三国中论奸雄算你曹操，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一派的假殷勤袖里藏刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "奉军令捉拿你怎肯相饶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "俺今日用兵时何必发笑"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "中了那小周郎苦肉计巧，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只烧得众兵丁皮开肉焦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "汉君侯若不信仔细观瞧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只剩下十八骑败兵来到"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小校，查看曹操还有多少人马。"
        },
        {
          "character": "小校",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你们站起了！一五，一十，十五，一、二、三！"
        },
        {
          "character": "小校",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十八骑残兵败将！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "军师吓，军师！你既能算，却不能料：慢说一十八骑残兵败将，就是一十八只"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "猛虎，何足道哉！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "料想他好一似鳌鱼吞钓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "伤弓鸟纵插翅也难飞逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "说什么我好似鳌鱼吞钓，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "说什么伤弓鸟也难飞逃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "上马金下马银筵酒美姣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你本是大义人怎忘故交？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "想当初待君侯恩高义好"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "官封你寿亭侯爵禄不少"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你虽然待我的恩高义好，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我亦曾答报了你的功劳："
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将印信悬高梁封金辞曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "斩颜良诛文丑立功报效"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我亦曾命人送文凭来到，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "临行时我又送美酒红袍。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "休提起送文凭令人可恼，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "诛孔秀，刺孟陶，王真被枭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "谢丞相假人情哪在心梢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "过黄河斩秦琪文凭才到"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在许昌曾许我云阳答报，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为什么把人情一旦搬抛？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "非是我忘却了云阳答报，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "因为你这奸曹罪恶难饶。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "挟天子命诸侯势压群僚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "董贵妃，马腾病，欲扶汉朝。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "上前来试一试偃月钢刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "在许田射鹿时把君欺藐"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "逼死了董贵妃其罪非小"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "恨不得拿住了剥皮削草"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曹孟德在马上苦苦哀告，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "君侯吓！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你何不留美名万古留标。"
